Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的交往可以更进一步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下，有特别通信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百…百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.26,0:07:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 我已经切换成独立频道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:07:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人会听见的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以谈谈吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的对手
