Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那样强大的武器，所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.30,0:08:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好担心好担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要安全归来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 有谁会传特别通讯的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.98,0:08:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我这样说你会觉得我是傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得如果你平安回来的话 我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往可以更进一步吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴 明人也有一样的想法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我不对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做人不可以这样，请原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才荷梅就一直在呼叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没看到吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于注意到啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.85,0:08:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便当没什么味道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我准备了很多食物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.25,0:08:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说也用不着这么多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.59,0:09:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一流的厨师\N要能随时应付顾客的点菜这是铁则
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人，我们是伙伴伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你的了，天河
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.57,0:09:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能辜负女孩子的期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙真可恨，羡慕死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河明人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙真可恨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羡慕死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河明人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴白痴，全都是白痴
