Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事，凉子小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，天河 你还是笨笨的老样子吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.35,0:12:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啊，突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.78,0:12:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去，吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
