Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.54,0:12:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 两位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像青春连续剧的场面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过要我说的话好像有点不健康
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好不要受他的影响太大哦 凉子君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这什么意思?
