Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.61,0:14:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然资料不足，但情况很糟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.16,0:14:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多糟?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，非常糟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.04,0:14:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶，可恶
