Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.54,0:14:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少啰唆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶，可恶，可恶
