Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样，满意了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.56,0:15:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有不好的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹节虫开始动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于资料不足
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.48,0:15:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法确知微黑洞弹何时发射
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.30,0:15:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过可以确定一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次受创将更严重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.62,0:15:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次的微黑洞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因飞出太空之后自然蒸发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.91,0:15:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以受害只有最小程度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次一定会在大气中蒸发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.35,0:15:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确定不会有错吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人可也不是白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个结果会变成怎样呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.32,0:15:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膨大的放射热在一瞬间将都市蒸发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃过这一劫的地方也会有强烈的迦玛射线
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战模式从A改成D
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.01,0:15:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要平安归来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.81,0:15:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不回来可伤脑筋了 我们可动弹不得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:16:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊，电瓶已经全给他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑开得太过份了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.51,0:16:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能源跟弹药所剩不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后不准给我擅自行动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.46,0:16:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.15,0:16:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好神气的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什，什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.22,0:16:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来跟过去的玩具不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.61,0:16:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTI配备有吸着地雷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了，我正在做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光，地雷还没好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.21,0:16:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，拿下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.09,0:17:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的AESTI
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.09,0:17:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战车车体底部是装甲最薄的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.05,0:17:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以瞄准备车身的底部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.61,0:17:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车身是指战车的车体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不是指船的船体哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲吻眼睛，命中\N(音同亲吻眼睛)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样，诸君?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.96,0:17:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实地攻击弱点就算空手打倒也有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀，好厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人刮目相看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急连络，赶快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说要逃 可是小AESTI也动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.63,0:17:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 刚才状况变得危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.68,0:17:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，不要急
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.27,0:17:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么办才好?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在竹节虫周围的空间重力波的变动增大中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.08,0:18:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来不及修理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.97,0:18:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办，怎么办才好?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去要怎么向司令部报告啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.73,0:18:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督，非常谢谢您的协助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越紧急时愈是坚强啊 我们的舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.44,0:18:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她对成员有信心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样直接冲到竹节虫去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吗 天河君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我知道，可是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷入苦战啦，你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,0:18:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之大家是伙伴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，就这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么做?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.43,0:18:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法，天河君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人负责直接去竹节虫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.51,0:18:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我们负责在这里阻止战车
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.56,0:18:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么就是这样?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:18:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去收拾竹节虫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.93,0:18:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们去收拾战车
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.59,0:19:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LET'S GO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.47,0:19:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家抓稳了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.47,0:19:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用撞的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出所料 就算阻止她也不会听的个性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.10,0:19:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在，走开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨大战车要这样对付吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.42,0:19:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么搞的?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.69,0:19:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好极了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.14,0:19:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.32,0:19:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"辅助电池剩一点"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快到了，马上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.05,0:19:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全炮发射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.61,0:19:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候不浪费子弹的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.34,0:19:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶，还是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不是说了不要浪费子弹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"可惜，补助电池用完了"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.52,0:20:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了，辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好干得好，做得太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是赤月，作战终了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.43,0:20:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能够来接我们那最好不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.81,0:20:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有许多枝节
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.71,0:20:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过辛苦了，天河明人君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.85,0:20:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经想好下一本同人志的标题了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用"男人的友情天地"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.60,0:20:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的感动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.45,0:21:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有纯粹的情感沉睡其中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要追寻梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容与泪水的数目就会渐渐增多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.93,0:21:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时想要更像自我地去感受风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.51,0:21:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不属于其他人的我自己的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.45,0:21:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要去发掘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"很久很久以前"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,0:21:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么，要我帮忙办人气投票?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.33,0:21:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"思兼这么说过"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.23,0:21:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是凑小姐成熟的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.56,0:21:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，小光的眼镜也实在不错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.79,0:21:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"我是机械?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"还是人类?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.26,0:21:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，还是舰长的胸部漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.43,0:21:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴白痴…呵呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.40,0:21:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，我投星野琉璃一票
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.57,0:21:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"宇宙漫画的决定版"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此这般，次回，机动战舰抚子是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.04,0:22:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚本首藤刚志\N所呈献的星野琉璃传奇三部曲第二弹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.58,0:22:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"那忘不了的日子"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.78,0:22:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回也要大家一起投票·
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.15,0:22:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对，大家一起看哟!
